Text: Hi all - I burned this ISO to DVD and it plays great on the computer, but the DVD player won't recognize it. Never had a problem with ISOs playing on the DVD player, but 3 torrent ISOs so far won't play. What am I missing? Any tips would be greatly appreciated - thanks!
Never mind - it was the stupid PAL-NTSC nonsense. Converted to NTSC, but the conversion is too jumpy as it splits the difference between the two. Bought a cheap region-free player. All is good.
